    <item>
      <title>诸神的黄昏：北欧的末日预言与重生</title>
      <link>https://vanvj00001.github.io/hugoblox-blog/posts/norse/%E8%AF%B8%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%84%E6%98%8F/</link>
